lor='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma' size='2'>Mob Level</td><td width='499' align='left' bgcolor='#000000' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma'size='2'>24 - 26</td></tr><tr><td width='98' align='left' bgcolor='#21456B' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma' size='2'>Location</td><td width='499' align='left' bgcolor='#21456B' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma'size='2'>Sister Island</td></tr><tr><td width='98' align='left' bgcolor='#000000' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma' size='2'>Factions</td><td width='499' align='left' bgcolor='#000000' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma'size='2'>-KingTearisThex, -ClericsofTunare, +CrushboneOrcs, -SoldiersofTunare</td></tr><tr><td width='98' align='left' bgcolor='#21456B' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma' size='2'>Spells Used</td><td width='499' align='left' bgcolor='#21456B' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma'size='2'>Drain Life spell, Darkness spell, Blood spell, Vampiric Curse</td></tr><tr><td width='98' align='left' bgcolor='#000000' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma' size='2'>Strategy</td><td width='499' align='left' bgcolor='#000000' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma'size='2'>After coming off the boat head off to the left and camp the spot just before the water, you can pull the sister at the tree 1st , I cast darkness then send the pet in , wait a bit , hit her with a boil blood then heal pet if needed, you can also pull the dock sister the same way BUT don't cast on her while she is in the water as the spell wont have an effect, above you are 2 more sisters in a hut, you can use terror on them to just pull 1 just walk up to the hut "don't get too close" open the door target one then move back to you camp spot and cast, but if its resisted you ~could~ be in trouble- send the pet in and get back to your spot and make sure you dark them both and Boil/Vampiric the one the pet isn't on ,, if she doesn't start coming after you ,, hit her with a venom and she will start chasing you , but with dark on you can keep out the way of her and if needed feign death , at this time the pet should of taken the one he was on down, if not , feign death and let the one on you go back to your pet and throw a boil on the one your pet is fighting, or a mend bones if the pet needs it , its also good to put a leather skin on before you attempt this , but it really isn't that hard, if in a group you can also pull the 2 in the vendor hut the same way, just cast on anyone but the non vendor and just the 2 around her should come, you don't want the vendor as she hits very hard, the exp here is awesome but of course you will take a few faction hits with this, but me being a DE necro it doesn't worry me at all.<br><br>

Believe me , this is a great spot and ive never seen anyone else doing this, maybe that will change now :)</td></tr><tr><td width='98' align='left' bgcolor='#21456B' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma' size='2'>Author</td><td width='499' align='left' bgcolor='#21456B' height='22' valign='middle'><font color='#FFFFFF' face='Tahoma'size='2'><a href ='mailto:kaldarin@the-bro.co.uk'>Skira</td></tr><tr></table><br><br></table></div>